title: BREAKING: Moorgate Underground Station 'EVACUATED due to security alert'
text:
BREAKING: Moorgate Underground Station 'EVACUATED due to security alert' BREAKING: Moorgate Underground Station 'EVACUATED due to security alert' EMERGENCY services have evacuated Moorgate Underground Station due to an imminent security threat. PUBLISHED: 16:07, Wed, Feb 22, 2017 | UPDATED: 16:11, Wed, Feb 22, 2017 
A suspect package has been discovered at the station, prompting hundreds of commuters to be rushed out of the major station to be evacutated. 
More to follow...
